#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:43
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:43"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:43
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:43"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Added numeric path segments for array indexing."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - Added numeric path segments for array indexing."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:47
msgid ""
"`ptool.toml.get(input, path)` reads the value at a specified path from TOML "
"text."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.toml.get(input, path)` lê o valor em um caminho especificado dentro "
"de um texto TOML."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:50
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:50"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The TOML text."
msgstr "`input` (string, obrigatório): O texto TOML."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:51
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:51"
msgid ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], required): A non-empty path array, such as `{"
"\"package\", \"version\"}` or `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`."
msgstr ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], obrigatório): Um array de caminho não vazio, "
"como `{\"package\", \"version\"}` ou `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:53
msgid ""
"Returns: The corresponding Lua value, or `nil` if the path does not exist."
msgstr "Retorna: O valor Lua correspondente, ou `nil` se o caminho não existir."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:55
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:55"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "Comportamento:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:57
msgid "String path segments select table keys."
msgstr "Segmentos de caminho do tipo string selecionam chaves de tabela."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:58
msgid ""
"Integer path segments select array elements using Lua's 1-based indexing."
msgstr ""
"Segmentos de caminho do tipo integer selecionam elementos de array usando o "
"índice base 1 do Lua."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/toml.md:60
